sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Gateway as Payment Gateway
    participant K as Kafka (Event)
    participant B as BookingService
    participant RMQ as RabbitMQ (Poll)
    participant DB as Postgres
    participant P as PaymentAPI (Feign)

    Note over Gateway, K: Path A: Event-Driven Callback (Fast)
    Gateway->>K: Payment Status Changed
    K->>B: pay-event (SUCCESS/FAILED)
    
    B->>DB: Update (if status=PROCESSING)
    alt Update Success
        B->>DB: Confirm Seats & Booking
        Note over B: Transaction Committed
    else Already processed (0 rows)
        Note over B: Ignore Duplicate (Race Winner)
    end

    Note over RMQ, B: Path B: Scheduled Polling (Fallback/Slow)
    RMQ->>B: Trigger Poll Cycle
    
    B->>DB: Find Booking & Check Status
    alt Not in PROCESSING (Early Exit)
        Note over B: Kafka already finished. Stop Polling.
    else Still PROCESSING
        B->>P: GET /v1/payments/status/{bookingId}
        P-->>B: PaymentStatus (SUCCESS/FAILED)
        
        B->>DB: Update (if status=PROCESSING)
        alt Update Success
            B->>DB: Confirm Seats & Booking
        end
    end
